code: export function parseJwt(token){if(!token){return;}var base64Url=token.split('.')[1];var base64=base64Url.replace('-','+').replace('_','/');return JSON.parse(window.atob(base64));}export var handleLogError=function handleLogError(error){if(error.response){console.log(error.response.data);}else if(error.request){console.log(error.request);}else{console.log(error.message);}};
